channel.title: Basic Winterlove Server
channel.description:
It's blank, it's basic, it's fairly stable. Before you do say something offensive, I didn't put much effort into this server. [b]This is only version 1, I have not added half the things I need to.[/b] [b]Information [/b] The server was developed for education purposed, I've had fun doing this server so I have decided to release and further the development while I ain't doing any clients. The server is really basic, it is a Winterlove server but It has some features and is more stable than Winterlove servers with the same features. As stated before this is only version one, the next version will have many more features like the thread per client, common winterlove exception glitches and a few more skills. I hope you enjoy this server, hopefully you will develop off it and start releasing your own. [b]Download[/b] http://uppit.com/v/12MHC233 [b]Pictures[/b] [b]I will not[/b] provide you with any pictures of the server, download and look for yourself, I don't see the point in posting pictures for a blank server with a few modifications. If you wish to post any pictures, feel free to do so. [b]Licence[/b]
This program is free software: you can redistribute it and/or modify it under the terms of the GNU General Public License as published by the Free Software Foundation, either version 3 of the License, or (at your option) any later version. This program is distributed in the hope that it will be useful, but WITHOUT ANY WARRANTY; without even the implied warranty of MERCHANTABILITY or FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE. See the GNU General Public License for more details. You should have received a copy of the GNU General Public License along with this program. If not, see .
[b]Anti leech[/b] There's a anti leech on the server, the hint is Player saving and loading, if you cannot work this out you are not worthy. [b]Credits[/b] Pablo - 317 deob editor. Moparisthebest - 317 deob. wL - Original server creator. [b]Jukk[/b] - Edited a few things. _Ikram - I work for him :eek:
